episodes.title: Cult leaders Masquerading as a church pastors and Bishops
episodes.description:
Paul Mackenzie is a self-proclaimed pastor who finds himself at the center of one of the most horrifying cult-related tragedies in recent history. De-Graft Amoako dive deep on the Kenyan cult-leader Paul Mackenzie and the reason behind his actions. #panafricanism #kenya  #paulmackenzie
